  "title": "Senior /Geotechnical Engineer",
  "description": "<h5><strong>Responsible for the execution of geotechnical designs involving the preparation of calculations and reviewing of geotechnical design drawings in accordance to customers' specifications, applicable codes and standards.</strong></h5>\n<p><strong>Job description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Ensure quality and accuracy of designs</li>\n  <li>Produce sketch drawings</li>\n  <li>Carry out design calculations</li>\n  <li>Ensure compliance with project Design Criteria/Client Brief/ Approved Concept</li>\n  <li>Check documentation complies with design</li>\n  <li>Attend design, clients, architects and site meetings</li>\n  <li>Ensure compliance with ISO Quality Procedure Manual</li>\n  <li>Ensure design output sustains continuity of drafting program.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Preferably 2 years experience in geotechnical design in a consultancy company</li>\n  <li>Candidate must possess a Bachelor's or Master's Degree in Geotechnical or Civil Engineering</li>\n</ul>",
